Special Powers
LE FAY'S BLESSING: Battle Fury. Dark Britain can reduce penetrating damage.
TAKE THE TRINKET, I BEG THEE…PLEASE: When Dark Britain is KO'd, choose a friendly character. For the rest of the game that character can use [Wing symbol], Toughness, Willpower, and Super Strength.
SLAY THE PRETENDER: Charge, Flurry, [Improved Movement: Hindering].
DIE, WITCHBREED: Blades/Claws/Fangs. // When Dark Britain hits, after resolutions choose one: remove an action token from him -or- heal 1 click. If the target has the X-Men keyword, choose both.

September 4, 2021
BLsquared
Got to see this knight shine against Old Man Phoenix. Was running an Armor theme team with Gwen of Arc and AzBats, just for fun at a casual event. Then, lol and behold, one guy built an X-Men team with OMP, Apocalypse Rogue, and Archangel. The match was going all right, he kept his Logan in the back at first, before Batman got a lucky Blades roll on Archangel. Then Batman was almost smitten, his long dial being his only saving grace, before Rogue finished him. Gwen attacked Rogue, and Britain followed up, but not before taking a flurry from Logan. Before long, it was just full dial Logan and Britain, who was 3 clicks from KO. The Logan player got super smug, saying I had no chance, but I decided that Britain was going to go out fighting. And fight he did, like a true warrior! It was a long battle, the duel between them, due to the healing from both, but eventually, I just kept picking Exploit instead of Flurry (this was before the WW rules), and rolling blades. Britain managed to heal up to his 2nd click, before finally slaying the monster, and my opponent was dumbfounded. One of the must epic moments I have had in a while. I love this figure so much, and even more so now. The new rules make him even better with the power combos, and giving him Herald of Galactus (which I didn't do that game, but is still a good idea) for the Willpower makes the OMA capability even better. I just wish he had at least Sidestep on those Flurry clicks, but you can't have them all lol.
